                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t18291029-146-off818 t18291029-146-crimeloc821"></join>. On the 9th of October I was informed a pair of trousers had been stolen- I went out and saw the prisoner running in the road, about twenty yards from my master's; I pursued, and saw him throw the trousers down - he ran through several street, but was overtaken and brought back; I am sure he is the person - they hung on the door post.</p>
